{"id": "1193169688302190725", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "When it was officially announced that Daphdale was going to be weakened, it was noted that there was negative sentiment among the player base", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:30:21.712000+00:00"}
{"id": "1193169917768388679", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "Therefore, the game planner has provided a channel for players to have a conversation with them to discuss matters related to weakening", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:31:16.421000+00:00"}
{"id": "1193170230457925652", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "However, for some reason, after collecting feedback and opinions from players, the planner may propose several adjustment plans, and the most objectionable items of players remain the same", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:32:30.972000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🕊️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1193173411485208577", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "This is the main reason", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:45:09.388000+00:00"}
{"id": "1193175716850843729", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "Another major reason is that some players feel that the official compensation is not enough to make up for the lack of resources they have invested in Daphdale and related team characters", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:54:19.030000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🕊️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1193176023693541386", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "The official response to this has been too slow and unrealistic", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:55:32.187000+00:00"}
{"id": "1193176111664873492", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "content": "That's why those players are so emotional", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T12:55:53.161000+00:00"}
